{"tid":623384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日笑話] 習近平：重新組建國家知識產權局　加大執法力度","createTime":"2018-04-10T03:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T06:37:58.000Z","uid":42921,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b5acfb091c9b4f5ff7dbf3c8b74f4511ecfd02","tid":623384,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平在博鰲亞洲論壇開幕式，公布擴大開放的舉措，包括要加強知識產權的保護。他說，這是完善產權保護制度最重要的內容，也是提高中國經濟競爭力最大的激勵。<br />\n<br />\n習近平表示，外資企業對加強保護知識產權有要求，中國企業對此更有要求，今年中國將重新組建國家知識產權局，加大執法力度。<br />\n<br />\n習近平又說，鼓勵中外企業開展正常技術交流合作，保護在華外資企業合法知識產權，同時希望外國政府加強對中國知識產權的保護。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ab9ec8526c0bed3f10b4fc5c0a2a0219030046","tid":623384,"uid":22609,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"全面判外國原創公司侵權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15050f4008d4a1f5fdeffb10038473559ab3b861","tid":623384,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"呢d野講左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8fb2ec328e2f38ab2acadbfd4b8bdab3c5be8d","tid":623384,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"咁快跪低"},{"pid":"8df61da3c956b84dacd06a2c011f4d8fcc3559f1","tid":623384,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"38f82b20fb989bf681ebf2c60ef6f73286a73773","tid":623384,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:14:20.000Z","msg":"外國膠一定好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />